<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='https://anovademocracia.com.br/images/0-2021/10/luta-pela-terra/cobertura-exclusiva-rondonia-7.webp' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='7583941941923273253' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='7788255247508958133' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='7788255247508958133'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://brasilmfp.blogspot.com/2021/10/ro-essas-terras-sao-do-povo-e-lutaremos.html'>RO: &#8216;Essas terras são do povo e lutaremos por elas&#8217;, afirmam camponeses enquanto PM e Força Nacional preparam massacre</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-7788255247508958133' itemprop='articleBody'>
<p>&#160;</p><h2 itemprop="name" style="border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: &quot;PT Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0.6em 0px 0.5em; position: relative;">Notícia reproduzida do Jornal A Nova Democracia:</h2><div style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); padding-top: 8px;"><br style="background-color: #fcfbf5; color: #191919; font-family: Ubuntu; font-size: 13px;"></div><dd class="createdby" itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #666666; display: inline-block; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.42857; list-style: none; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 5px; text-transform: uppercase;">&#160;<span data-original-title="" data-toggle="tooltip" itemprop="name" style="box-sizing: border-box;" title="">TAÍS SOUZA</span></dd><span face="Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif" style="background-color: white; color: #666666; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase;">&#160;</span><time data-original-title="Data de Publicação" data-toggle="tooltip" datetime="2021-10-11T13:49:41-03:00" itemprop="datePublished" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #666666; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase;" title="">11 OUTUBRO 2021</time><div class="entry-header" style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 30px; position: relative;"><h2 itemprop="name" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: &quot;PT Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; margin: 8px 0px 0px;">RO: &#8216;Essas terras são do povo e lutaremos por elas&#8217;, afirmam camponeses enquanto PM e Força Nacional preparam massacre</h2></div><div itemprop="articleBody" style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5em; margin: 10px 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: justify;"><img alt="" src="https://anovademocracia.com.br/images/0-2021/10/luta-pela-terra/cobertura-exclusiva-rondonia-7.webp" style="border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;"></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5em; margin: 10px 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: justify;"><span class="legenda" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #666666; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 20px;">Assembleia Popular das Áreas Tiago Campin dos Santos e Ademar Ferreira, 02 de outubro de 2021. Foto: Resistência Camponesa</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5em; margin: 10px 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><img alt="" src="https://anovademocracia.com.br/images/0-2021/10/luta-pela-terra/tiago_santos_1.webp" style="border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;"></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5em; margin: 10px 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: justify;"><span class="legenda" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #666666; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 20px;">Durante a AP as famílias declaram: &quot;Não sairemos daqui, essas terras são do povo e lutaremos por elas&quot;. Foto: Resistência Camponesa<span></span></span></p></div>
